data.description: Modern Boise living in a beautiful, mature neighborhood! This single-level home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1848 sq ft of comfort. The functional split bedroom floor plan, high ceilings, solid surface counters and oversized windows create an airy ambiance with lots of natural light. Enjoy a large fenced yard with a generously sized covered patio, perfect for outdoor gatherings. The oversized 2-car garage, solid surface countertops and short distance from community pool are just a few of the features that offer a blend of convenience and luxury. A perfect fit!
